  - G4/TechTV

"One of the biggest online text-based games."
  - Wired.com

"I don't believe there's another game in existence with this much depth."
  - John Romero, co-designer of Doom and Quake

"Few virtual worlds with an immensely complicated combat system avoid being
completely dominated by it -- Achaea is the best-known exception."
  - Dr. Richard Bartle, inventor of MUD
